ActRoyal Canadian Mint Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of GHISLAIN HARVEY of Ville de la Baie, Quebec, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Royal Canadian Mint to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Judith Kavanagh, whose term has expired.
